  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">LRF: Legal Aid Project December 2009-2011. On the short term: - strengthen the governance and finance function of LRF. On the long term: 1. To provide legal assistance to indigent persons. 2. To provide litigation services to vulnerable persons. 3. To inform the public of legal and human rights more effectively. 4. To ensure that LRF operates efficiently and effectively. 5. To enhance the quality of legal aid services and programmes. 6. To strengthen collaborations and strategic partnerships.</narrative>
